Investor






Company Profile
American Renal Associates Holdings, Inc. (ARA) is a leading provider of outpatient dialysis services in the United States. Since its inception, ARA has been the pioneer in physician partnerships focused on excellent patient care. As of March 31, 2017, ARA operated 217 dialysis clinics exclusively through its physician partnership model with local nephrologists.






